chart_description: The cgroup.net_packets chart displays the number of packets sent or received per second on network interfaces associated with the cgroup.

dimension_descriptions.multicast: The number of multicast packets sent or received per second on the network interfaces associated with the cgroup.
dimension_descriptions.received: The number of received packets per second on the network interfaces associated with the cgroup.
dimension_descriptions.sent: The number of sent packets per second on the network interfaces associated with the cgroup.
